==Definition==

<b>irrational</b> (<i>noun</i>)
# (<i>mathematics</i>) An [[irrational_number]]; a number incapable of being written as a fraction of two [[integers]].
:Ex. [[e]], [[pi]]
<b>irrational</b>
# Not [[rational]].
# Unfounded or [[nonsensical]].
:Ex. <i>Irrational decision</i>, <i>irrational action</i>


